Subject to this license, Nana Aboagye Boateng grants the customer a limited,
non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to use QQueue Cloud only if
the customer has an active paid commercial or self-hosted license, or explicit
written permission from Nana Aboagye Boateng.

2. Permitted Use

The customer may use QQueue Cloud internally for the customer's own business
operations during the active license term.

Authorized employees and contractors may access QQueue Cloud only as needed to
support the customer's internal use. The customer is responsible for those
employees' and contractors' compliance with this license.

Trial or evaluation use is allowed for up to 30 days unless Nana Aboagye Boateng extends
the trial or evaluation period in writing.

3. Restrictions

Unless explicitly allowed in writing by Nana Aboagye Boateng, the customer may not:

- redistribute, sublicense, resell, publish, share, lease, rent, lend, or
